    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>There is no reason for the black box to be packaged with a surveillance device that records viewing choices. No, thanks. I will await the arrival of the improved VCR, without the surveillance feature.</p>
        <p>John Shaw  Springfield, Pa.</p>
